Good, Oscar.

23
00:02:41,730 --> 00:02:43,250
If that so,

24
00:02:43,250 --> 00:02:44,520
tomorrow morning,

25
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,850
Teacher Zhao Wu Ji will lead you...

26
00:02:46,850 --> 00:02:48,790
to the Star Dou Forest.

27
