Unless you meet a Millennium Soul Beast,

29
00:02:53,460 --> 00:02:54,940
or else I’ll not interfere.

30
00:02:54,940 --> 00:02:57,500
You have to think of strategies on the way.

31
00:02:57,500 --> 00:02:59,550
How arrogant you are!

32
00:02:59,550 --> 00:03:00,870
Teach them a lesson!

33
00:03:00,870 --> 00:03:03,250
A fight? I love it.

34
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:06,690
Our turn!

35
00:03:08,340 --> 00:03:13,010
[Soul Land]
[Episode 21]

36
00:03:23,070 --> 00:03:26,050
I’m Ye Zhi Qiu, head of foreign affairs
department of Cang Hui School.

37
00:03:26,050 --> 00:03:28,520
Which clan are you from?

38
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,890
We’re from Shrek School.

39
00:03:30,890 --> 00:03:35,550
Shrek? Never heard of it.

40
00:03:35,550 --> 00:03:37,410
Because you’re ignorant.

41
00:03:37,410 --> 00:03:41,130
<i>These little monsters don’t
look like a clan’s disciples.</i>

42
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,920
<i>Soul King ranking above Level 50.</i>

43
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:07,680
<i>I have to use my hidden weapons.</i>

44
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:10,290
<i>Black Turtle Beast Soul.</i>

45
00:04:10,290 --> 00:04:14,570
Where is your teacher?
Let the adults settle this.

46
00:04:14,570 --> 00:04:15,840
You’re just an old tortoise,

47
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,460
how dare you ask to see our teacher?

48
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:19,830
We can settle you easily.

49
00:04:19,830 --> 00:04:21,180
What did you say?

50
00:04:22,650 --> 00:04:27,390
Good, I’ll teach you a lesson
on behalf of your teacher.

51
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,420
Respective customers,

52
00:04:32,420 --> 00:04:36,360
please do not fight in the shop...

53
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:39,380
I’ll wait for you outside.

54
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:41,390
His Martial Soul is Black Turtle.

55
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:43,930
I’m certain that
he’s a defense type war soul master.

56
00:04:43,930 --> 00:04:46,230
Strong in defense, weak in attack.

57
00:04:46,230 --> 00:04:47,410
We may win.

58
00:04:47,410 --> 00:04:49,290
Zhu Qing, Mu Bai and me.

59
00:04:49,290 --> 00:04:51,570
Three of us are fast, we’ll pin down him.

60
00:04:51,570 --> 00:04:53,200
Xiao Wu will support us.

61
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,330
Black Turtle corresponds to water.

62
00:04:54,330 --> 00:04:56,740
Fatty’s Phoenix Fire restraints it.

63
00:04:56,740 --> 00:04:59,740
Water restraints fire,
vice versa, fire restraints water.

64
00:04:59,740 --> 00:05:01,970
You’ll attack at the outer area.

65
00:05:01,970 --> 00:05:04,090
Sausage Oscar will aid Fatty.

66
00:05:04,090 --> 00:05:04,740
We’re outnumber.

67
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,100
Let’s play a protracted fight.

68
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:06,990
Tang San,

69
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:08,060
what about me?

70
00:05:10,270 --> 00:05:10,870
Well...

71
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,500
your Martial Soul is special,

72
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:13,900
you’ll play by ear then.

73
00:05:16,290 --> 00:05:17,380
Let’s go.

74
00:05:26,450 --> 00:05:28,150
If you want recognition,

75
00:05:28,150 --> 00:05:32,450
then prove it to them
with actions that you belong to Shrek School.

76
00:05:42,050 --> 00:05:46,590
Come on, Teacher.

77
00:05:47,290 --> 00:05:52,020
Come on, Teacher.

78
00:05:52,020 --> 00:05:53,850
I’ll give you another chance.

79
00:05:53,850 --> 00:05:56,480
It’s still not too late to apologize.

80
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:59,520
Beat us first then.

81
00:06:00,890 --> 00:06:04,680
Let me teach you how to be a human.

82
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:07,710
Remember, we’re not human,

83
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,570
but monsters.

84
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:27,930
Come on, Teacher.

85
00:06:27,930 --> 00:06:30,050
First soul skill,

86
00:06:31,460 --> 00:06:32,800
White Tiger...

87
00:06:35,980 --> 00:06:37,450
Intense Light...

88
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:45,250
Wave.

89
00:06:51,310 --> 00:06:52,730
First soul skill,

90
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,030
Intertwine...

91
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,330
Ma Hong Jun.

92
00:07:20,130 --> 00:07:21,150
He’s great.

93
00:07:21,150 --> 00:07:22,380
It’s over already?

94
00:07:23,470 --> 00:07:24,960
Grilled tortoise.

95
00:07:27,100 --> 00:07:29,110
<i>No, there’s cold air.</i>

96
00:07:29,110 --> 00:07:32,210
First soul skill,
Black Turtle Protection Shield.

97
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:35,200
Stop him.

98
00:07:35,410 --> 00:07:37,030
White Tiger Intensive Light Wave.

99
00:07:39,410 --> 00:07:41,860
<i>Black Turtle’s defense is really powerful.</i>

100
00:07:42,740 --> 00:07:45,770
Second soul skill, Dark Water Ice Bound.

101
00:07:45,770 --> 00:07:47,680
<i>He uses two soul skills from the start.</i>

102
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:50,020
<i>I’ll not let you end this fight so soon.</i>

103
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:55,650
Nether Spikes.

104
00:07:55,650 --> 00:07:57,240
Black Turtle Protection Shield.

105
00:07:58,610 --> 00:08:00,170
What is this?

106
00:08:00,170 --> 00:08:01,370
He shrinks into his shell.

107
00:08:01,370 --> 00:08:02,420
Unbelievable, right?

108
00:08:02,420 --> 00:08:03,730
My hand is stuck.

109
00:08:03,730 --> 00:08:07,070
Third soul skill, Dark Water...

110
00:08:07,070 --> 00:08:08,080
Don’t you dare!

111
00:08:10,150 --> 00:08:11,180
Intertwine.

112
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:17,680
Dark Water Rage.

113
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:22,650
- He’s trying to isolate my coldness.
- Dai Mu Bai.

114
00:08:22,650 --> 00:08:25,930
Too bad your soul power
is at least ten levels lower than mine.

115
00:08:25,930 --> 00:08:27,800
Oh, really?

116
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,610
White Tiger Protection Barrier.

117
00:08:37,790 --> 00:08:40,040
<i>My body is totally numb with cold.</i>

118
00:08:41,020 --> 00:08:42,000
Intertwine.

119
00:08:43,210 --> 00:08:44,570
Darn it.

120
00:08:49,470 --> 00:08:51,110
White Tiger Protection Barrier.

121
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:55,250
<i>Oh, no, I’m freezing.</i>

122
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:58,860
Fatty.

123
00:08:58,870 --> 00:09:00,510
Boss, well done.

124
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:07,300
I’ll kill you both!

125
00:09:22,050 --> 00:09:23,610
<i>Is it that I’ve made a false judgment?</i>

126
00:09:23,610 --> 00:09:25,490
<i>This Black Turtle is
not a defense type Martial Soul?</i>

127
00:09:26,780 --> 00:09:28,200
<i>These scoundrels...</i>

128
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:32,100
At this late hour,

129
00:09:32,700 --> 00:09:36,170
why are you out here instead of sleeping?

130
00:09:41,980 --> 00:09:44,110
Go back to sleep now.

131
00:09:54,310 --> 00:09:55,300
Wait.

132
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:57,300
What’s the matter?

133
00:09:57,300 --> 00:09:59,290
You’re their teacher, right?

134
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:00,870
Just now, your students

135
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,470
humiliated our school, Cang Hui School.

136
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:05,360
You need to give us an explanation.

137
00:10:06,670 --> 00:10:08,000
Explanation?

138
00:10:09,570 --> 00:10:11,040
What is there to explain?

139
00:10:15,070 --> 00:10:18,540
Cang Hui School always
bullies the weak and creates troubles.

140
00:10:19,040 --> 00:10:21,900
In my opinion, it’s a sucking school.

141
00:10:25,340 --> 00:10:26,940
You’re really useless.

142
00:10:27,470 --> 00:10:29,640
You can’t even handle a tortoise.

143
00:10:29,740 --> 00:10:32,300
I’ll settle you once we get back to school.

144
00:10:36,300 --> 00:10:37,240
Teacher Zhao,

145
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:38,700
behind you.

146
00:10:40,740 --> 00:10:42,300
Get back to sleep.

147
00:10:47,940 --> 00:10:49,840
We’ll talk using our strength.

148
00:11:13,670 --> 00:11:17,800
[Soul Land]

149
00:11:30,970 --> 00:11:32,370
<i>You didn’t even use your Martial Soul.</i>

150
00:11:32,940 --> 00:11:33,870
<i>So arrogant.</i>

151
00:12:00,330 --> 00:12:02,460
Teacher.

152
00:12:02,740 --> 00:12:07,550
Beating up people without
using Martial Soul is really enjoyable.

153
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:18,850
Teacher, are you okay?

154
00:12:31,070 --> 00:12:32,070
You are...

155
00:12:32,740 --> 00:12:34,040
really embarrassing.

156
00:12:36,830 --> 00:12:38,480
I’ll note this down.

157
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:42,410
After we’re back you’re going
to undergo a special training.

158
00:12:42,410 --> 00:12:45,130
Why didn’t you use
Martial Soul to aid the others just now?

159
00:12:45,830 --> 00:12:48,650
It wasn’t the right moment, I was waiting...

160
00:12:51,800 --> 00:12:52,770
Rong Rong...

161
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:56,340
was waiting for Mu Bai’s
White Tiger Vajra Transformation.

162
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:58,370
Right?

163
00:13:00,850 --> 00:13:01,770
Yes.

164
00:13:03,870 --> 00:13:05,340
Catch him off guard.

165
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:06,670
Good.

166
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,200
Remember,

167
00:13:08,770 --> 00:13:10,300
once you entered Shrek School,

168
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:12,000
you’re a team.

169
00:13:15,630 --> 00:13:16,370
Okay,

170
00:13:16,770 --> 00:13:18,070
get back to sleep.

171
00:13:18,070 --> 00:13:19,540
Okay, Teacher Zhao.

172
00:14:18,340 --> 00:14:22,840
Star Dou Forest is much greater
than those forests with reared soul beasts.

173
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:26,800
We’ll meet Millennium or Decade Millennium..

174
00:14:26,970 --> 00:14:28,070
Soul Beasts at any time.

175
00:14:38,900 --> 00:14:40,570
Upon entering the forest,

176
00:14:40,700 --> 00:14:43,100
you must stay at least twenty meters close to me.

177
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:45,570
Especially for Ning Rong Rong and Oscar.

178
00:14:46,070 --> 00:14:47,200
Both of you must be careful.

179
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:50,000
Without my permission,

180
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:52,570
no one is allowed to attack the soul beast,

181
00:14:53,070 --> 00:14:53,840
understand?

182
00:14:54,170 --> 00:14:54,800
Understand.

183
00:14:58,870 --> 00:14:59,440
Good.

184
00:15:00,100 --> 00:15:00,800
Let’s go.

185
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:03,200
Mu Bai, Tang San, clear the path.

186
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:43,370
Stop.

187
00:16:47,370 --> 00:16:48,000
What’s the matter?

188
00:16:49,340 --> 00:16:50,700
There are many low-level soul beasts here.

189
00:16:50,870 --> 00:16:51,800
Let’s take another way.

190
00:16:53,170 --> 00:16:54,440
Soul beast grows slowly.

191
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:56,100
Let’s avoid them if we can do so.

192
00:16:59,160 --> 00:17:00,340
If we kill or hurt them accidentally,

193
00:17:00,690 --> 00:17:03,270
in just a few years, no more soul beasts
will be here in the forest.

194
00:17:05,870 --> 00:17:06,470
Make sense.

195
00:17:06,970 --> 00:17:07,740
We shall take another way.

196
00:17:12,970 --> 00:17:14,070
One more reason,

197
00:17:14,800 --> 00:17:15,970
If we fight,

198
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:19,670
the smell of the blood and the sound
may attract powerful soul beasts.

199
00:17:20,910 --> 00:17:22,270
We’d better be careful.

200
00:17:24,140 --> 00:17:26,400
You’re quite knowledgeable.

201
00:17:26,670 --> 00:17:28,600
These are all taught by my master.

202
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:36,100
Let’s put our guards up.

203
00:17:55,770 --> 00:17:58,200
Watch out. Something is
heading to us in a high speed.

204
00:17:58,600 --> 00:18:00,800
Oscar, Ning Rong Rong, move closer.

205
00:18:07,690 --> 00:18:08,540
I’ll go on the tree to check.

206
00:18:16,540 --> 00:18:17,400
Did you see it?

207
00:18:17,700 --> 00:18:19,400
It seems to be a flying snake.

208
00:18:21,540 --> 00:18:22,900
Flying snake?

209
00:18:23,170 --> 00:18:24,270
What does it look like?

210
00:18:24,500 --> 00:18:25,600
I can’t see it clearly.

211
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:27,770
It flies closely to the ground,
two or three meters to the ground.

212
00:18:27,970 --> 00:18:29,570
It has a red crown on its head.

213
00:18:29,730 --> 00:18:31,340
What does its tail look like?

214
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:32,370
Its tail is

215
00:18:33,370 --> 00:18:34,270
shaped like a fan.

216
00:18:34,740 --> 00:18:36,300
It’s a Phoenix Tail Crest Serpent.

217
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:37,400
Haha.

218
00:18:37,600 --> 00:18:39,370
Oscar, you’re lucky.

219
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:42,140
But we don’t know how old this snake is.

220
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:44,370
Watch its direction carefully. Prepare to hunt.

221
00:18:45,940 --> 00:18:46,400
Zhu Qing,

222
00:18:46,940 --> 00:18:48,470
how long is the snake?

223
00:18:49,100 --> 00:18:50,100
What is the color of its wings?

224
00:18:51,700 --> 00:18:54,400
It’s about six to eight meters long.

225
00:18:54,600 --> 00:18:56,100
Wings are pale red.

226
00:18:58,740 --> 00:18:59,400
It’s coming.

227
00:20:46,030 --> 00:20:49,790
[Next Episode]

228
00:20:49,790 --> 00:20:51,410
Stop.

229
00:20:51,410 --> 00:20:53,410
We found this snake first.

230
00:20:53,410 --> 00:20:54,810
Return it to us.

231
00:20:54,810 --> 00:20:57,470
Or else, we’ll not be easy on you.

232
00:20:58,430 --> 00:21:01,240
A battle of soul power? Come on then.

